verificationCode.text:
Your Bananatalk verification code is: {code}

Enter this code in the app to verify your email address. It expires in {minutes} minutes.

If you didn't request this code, you can ignore this email — no account will be created.

passwordResetCode.text:
Your Bananatalk password reset code is: {code}

Enter this code in the app to choose a new password. It expires in {minutes} minutes.

If you didn't request a password reset, you can ignore this email — your password won't change.
